  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Aligns state and local procurement laws with federal law prohibiting the procurement of certain technology and electronic parts or products which are determined to pose a risk to state and national security; relates to the authority of the office of information technology services to issue certain guidance relating thereto."
    }
